## Installation

This study tries to answerr the Research Question: To what extent have Boston food safety inspection outcomes changed over time in terms of volume and severity, and are certain neighborhoods improving or worsening over the past 20 years?

# Data

The data used is [Food Establishment Inspections Boston Data](https://data.boston.gov/dataset/food-establishment-inspections), and was extracted initially on February 15 2026.

## Usage

In the files you will find a FinalProjectRunningNotebook Jupyter notebook with the code to run both the analysis, model, and all the graphics generated. 

PosterDS_CelesteDeudon is the final poster for the DS Capstone Presentation (presented on April 28th 2026) to show findings and process.

